  <header class="article-header">
    <h1>New 'Concussion' Trailer Is Another Look at Upcoming Film Starring Will Smith</h1>
    <div class="by-line">
      <a title="Chris Riotta's Profile" class="link-author avatar avatar-small" href="../../profiles/188862/chris-riotta">
        <img alt="Chris Riotta's avatar image" class="no-share-btns" src="http://media3.mic.com/NmU4NDY3ZTBkZiMvODVUZHVsb0hyM0J3OUszOUhCTUoyTDR5OUlRPS8yNXgyNS9zbWFydC9odHRwczovL3MzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20vcG9saWN5bWljLWltYWdlcy83NjEzYTg1NjMwMmYxZjViNjAzNDBiOWZkNjVkMzQ0ZmZmZDVjNWUwNTQ1Y2IzMzEyZGM5NTAwODUwZTM5NzM0LmpwZw==.jpg">
      </a>
      By
      <a title="Chris Riotta's Profile" class="link-author name" href="../../profiles/188862/chris-riotta">Chris Riotta</a>
      <time datetime="2015-11-06T21:33:48.000Z" pubdate="">November 06, 2015</time>
    </div>
    <div class="share-facebook-twitter subhead">
      <span class="fb-like-container-text">Like Mic on Facebook:</span>
      <span class="fb-button">
        <div class="fb-like-top fb-like" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/MicMedia" data-width="300" data-keen-tracking-name="subhed" data-keen-social-channel="facebook" data-show-faces="false" data-send="false" data-layout="button"></div>
      </span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div id="article-body" class="article-body share-media-toolbar-block"><div class="share-media share-media-side-fold">
